<head>
  <meta name="title" content="Southeast Breccia Fan (floor sub-space) (Potter Creek)"/>
  <meta name="description" content="The fan landform sloping from the SE end and coalescing at mid-chamber, its apex under the SE chimney, that it is structureless cemented breccia (lumped as stratum A), and the documented Arctotherium+Ursus surface occurrence."/>
  <meta name="rights" content="Interpretive: Footprint extent and apex height (read from the plan/section), exact slope and surface relief. LAYOUT: global_position/level_order/stream_bbox are interpretive staging for the unified walkable level, "/>
</head>
